# Component Registry Selection Guide

This project has **60+ component registries** configured in `components.json`. This guide helps AI assistants select the best components for different use cases.

## Registry Categories

### Core UI Components
**Registry**: `@shadcn` (default)
- **Use for**: Basic UI elements (buttons, cards, dialogs, forms, etc.)
- **When to use**: Standard UI needs, most common components
- **Examples**: Button, Card, Dialog, Input, Select, Table, Tabs

### Animation & Visual Effects
**Registries**: `@magicui`, `@aceternity`, `@motion-primitives`, `@animate-ui`
- **Use for**: Animated components, visual effects, transitions
- **When to use**: Need animations, hover effects, loading states, visual flair
- **Examples**: Animated gradients, particle effects, scroll animations, motion components

### Forms & Input
**Registries**: `@formcn`, `@shadcn`
- **Use for**: Form components, validation, input fields
- **When to use**: Building forms, data entry, validation
- **Examples**: Form builders, validated inputs, multi-step forms

### Data Display
**Registries**: `@shadcn`, `@blocks`, `@shadcnblocks`
- **Use for**: Tables, lists, data visualization, dashboards
- **When to use**: Displaying data, creating dashboards, data tables
- **Examples**: Data tables, charts, lists, grids

### AI & Chat Interfaces
**Registries**: `@assistant-ui`, `@ai-elements`, `@prompt-kit`
- **Use for**: AI chat interfaces, assistant UIs, prompt interfaces
- **When to use**: Building AI features, chat interfaces, assistant tools
- **Examples**: Chat interfaces, AI assistants, prompt builders

### Supabase Integration
**Registry**: `@supabase`
- **Use for**: Supabase-specific UI components
- **When to use**: Direct Supabase integration, auth UI, database UI
- **Examples**: Auth components, database viewers, Supabase-specific widgets

### Commerce & Payments
**Registries**: `@commercn`, `@billingsdk`, `@paykit-sdk`
- **Use for**: E-commerce, payments, billing, subscriptions
- **When to use**: Building commerce features, payment flows, billing
- **Examples**: Product cards, checkout flows, billing dashboards

### Specialized Features
- **`@clerk`**: Clerk authentication components
- **`@algolia`**: Algolia search components
- **`@plate`**: Rich text editor components
- **`@prosekit`**: Prose editor components
- **`@nuqs`**: URL state management components
